230вҶ’\section{Seed Triples: The $(0, a, b)$ Structure}
231вҶ’\label{sec:seeds}
232вҶ’%======================================================================
233вҶ’
234вҶ’\subsection{Analytical condition}
235вҶ’
236вҶ’For a triple $(0, \zch_a, \zch_b)$ with one massless member, the 
237вҶ’Koide ratio becomes:
238вҶ’\begin{equation}
239вҶ’Q = \frac{\zch_a^2 + \zch_b^2}{(\zch_a + \zch_b)^2}\,.

